From: ehanoc <ehanoc@protonmail.com>
Date: Sat, 25 Apr 2026 15:06:45 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] util: Allow for PCI root buses not numbered "0"
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
